{
  "text": "The orthonormal vierbeins on T M are then defined by the relation V a = \u03bbE a \u2208 \u0393(T M) where the conformal factor \u03bb is determined by g bab = V a ln \u03bb 2 . In the end, the Riemannian metric on a four-dimensional spacetime manifold M is given by [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] ",
